{
  "texts": [
    "Throughout training, slides and classes will be oversampled to enable this balancing.",
    "This mini-batch balancing can be customized or disabled.",
    "During training, one epoch is defined as the total number of image tiles available in the training dataset divided by the batch size.",
    "The user can specify the interval at which validation checks are performed in the middle of an epoch.",
    "Early stopping can be configured to trigger when the exponential moving average of either loss or accuracy plateaus, or models can be trained for a prespecified number of epochs."
  ]
}